<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871023-0167 </DOCNO><HL> PPG Industries Sale</HL><DD> 10/23/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> PPG XTENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM) </IN><DATELINE> PITTSBURGH  </DATELINE><TEXT>   PPG Industries Inc. said it agreed to sell its Michigan oil and gas operations to Marathon Oil Co., a subsidiary of USX Corp. Terms weren't disclosed. The sale is expected to be completed by year's end.    PPG produces glass, glass fiber, coatings and resins as well as specialty and industrial chemicals. </TEXT></DOC>